Yes, I think QuotaEnforcer would work for your purpose, as long as the 
300 limit is something you want to apply per host, server, or frontier 
&#39;group&#39; (ie queue).

QuotaEnforcer is a processor, and to use it insert it into the chain of 
processors before any fetchers, so that it has a chance to apply its 
processing-cancellation before the URI is fetched. For example, you 
could place it just after the Preselector.

- Gordon @ IA

